Properties.ProtectedString:
--[[ Fixed by ArceusInator 1/22/2015 Zombies no longer randomly die, works with FE --]]
----------------- --| Constants |-- -----------------
local NPC_ID = 93601062 -- Asset ID of the NPC to be launched
local COOLDOWN = 6 -- Seconds until tool can be used again local TIME_TO_LIVE = 60 -- Seconds until NPC is cleaned up
local LAUNCH_SPEED_MIN = 60 -- Minimum speed NPC will be launched local LAUNCH_SPEED_MAX = 300 -- Maximum speed NPC will be launched
local LAUNCH_TIME_MIN = 0 -- Seconds until launch speed starts increasing beyond min local LAUNCH_TIME_MAX = 3 -- Seconds to reach max launch speed
local CHANCE_TO_EXPLODE = 10 -- There is a 1 in X chance that the NPC will explode
local Tool = script.Parent while Tool:FindFirstChild('Handle') == nil do wait() end local ToolHandle = Tool.Handle
----------------- --| Variables |-- -----------------
local InsertService = Game:GetService('InsertService') local DebrisService = Game:GetService('Debris') local PlayersService = Game:GetService('Players')
local MyPlayer
local Npc = InsertService:LoadAsset(NPC_ID):GetChildren()[1] Npc:MakeJoints()
do -- Give NPC a creator tag local creatorTag = Instance.new('ObjectValue') creatorTag.Name = 'creator' creatorTag.Value = MyPlayer creatorTag.Parent = Npc end
local NpcClone = Npc:Clone() NpcClone:MakeJoints()
local Mouse = nil local ClickTime = 0
local SoundTable = {} local Holding = false
----------------- --| Functions |-- -----------------
local function OnButton1Down() local myModel = MyPlayer.Character if Tool.Enabled and myModel and myModel:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and myModel.Humanoid.Health > 0 then ClickTime = time() Holding = true end end
local function OnButton1Up(hitCF) if not Holding then return end
Holding = false local myModel = MyPlayer.Character if Tool.Enabled and myModel and myModel:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and myModel.Humanoid.Health > 0 then Tool.Enabled = false
-- Determine launch speed (based on how long click is held) local launchSpeed = LAUNCH_SPEED_MIN do local timeHeldDown = time() - ClickTime if timeHeldDown > LAUNCH_TIME_MIN then local speedRange = LAUNCH_SPEED_MAX - LAUNCH_SPEED_MIN local timeRatio = timeHeldDown / (LAUNCH_TIME_MAX - LAUNCH_TIME_MIN) launchSpeed = launchSpeed + (speedRange * math.min(timeRatio, 1)) end end
-- Give all the NPC's BaseParts a velocity, and make any Humanoids sit local velocity = (hitCF.p - ToolHandle.CFrame.p).unit * launchSpeed for _, child in pairs(NpcClone:GetChildren()) do if child:IsA('BasePart') then child.Velocity = velocity elseif child:IsA('Humanoid') then child.Sit = true --NOTE: Turns off the gyro until NPC jumps end end
-- Add the explode script if we get lucky if math.random(CHANCE_TO_EXPLODE) == 1 then local explodeScript = script:FindFirstChild('Explode') if explodeScript then local explodeScriptClone = explodeScript:Clone() explodeScriptClone.Parent = NpcClone explodeScriptClone.Disabled = false end end
-- Add the NPC to the world DebrisService:AddItem(NpcClone, TIME_TO_LIVE) NpcClone.Parent = Workspace NpcClone.creator.Value = MyPlayer NpcClone:MakeJoints() NpcClone:MoveTo(ToolHandle.Position) --NOTE: Must already be in Workspace NpcClone:MakeJoints()
-- Clone the next NPC NpcClone = Npc:Clone() NpcClone:MakeJoints()
wait(COOLDOWN)
Tool.Enabled = true end end
local function OnEquipped() MyPlayer = PlayersService:GetPlayerFromCharacter(Tool.Parent) end
------------------- --| Remotes |-- -------------------
Tool.MouseButton1Down.OnServerEvent:connect(function(client) if client == MyPlayer then OnButton1Down() end end) Tool.MouseButton1Up.OnServerEvent:connect(function(client, hitCF) if client == MyPlayer then OnButton1Up(hitCF) end end)
-------------------- --| Script Logic |-- --------------------
Tool.Equipped:connect(OnEquipped)

local Model = script.Parent
local BodyColors = Model:FindFirstChild('Body Colors') if BodyColors then -- Make BodyColors red local red = BrickColor.new('Bright red') BodyColors.HeadColor = red BodyColors.LeftArmColor = red BodyColors.LeftLegColor = red BodyColors.RightArmColor = red BodyColors.RightLegColor = red BodyColors.TorsoColor = red end
local HeadMesh = nil do -- Find HeadMesh local head = Model:FindFirstChild('Head') if head then HeadMesh = head:FindFirstChild('Mesh') end end
-- Head flashy if HeadMesh then local color = HeadMesh.VertexColor local red = Vector3.new(2, 0, 0) local function flashy(howLong) HeadMesh.VertexColor = red wait(howLong) HeadMesh.VertexColor = color wait(howLong) end local flashTime = 1 while flashTime > 0.025 do flashy(flashTime) flashTime = flashTime * 0.75 end else wait(3) end
Instance.new('Explosion', Workspace).Position = Model:GetModelCFrame().p
local BoomSound = script:FindFirstChild('Boom') if BoomSound then local torso = Model:FindFirstChild('Torso') if torso then BoomSound.Parent = torso end BoomSound:Play() end

----------------- --| Constants |-- -----------------
local Tool = script.Parent while Tool:FindFirstChild('Handle') == nil do wait() end local ToolHandle = Tool.Handle
local MOUSE_ICON = 'rbxasset://textures/GunCursor.png' local RELOADING_ICON = 'rbxasset://textures/GunWaitCursor.png'
local COOLDOWN = 6 -- Seconds until tool can be used again
----------------- --| Variables |-- -----------------
local MyPlayer = game:GetService'Players'.LocalPlayer
local Mouse = nil local ClickTime = 0
local SoundTable = {} local Holding = false
----------------- --| Functions |-- -----------------
local function StartInfiniteChargeSound() local chargeSound = ToolHandle:FindFirstChild('Charge') local lastPlayTime = 0 repeat -- Start a new charge sound every second if chargeSound and time() - lastPlayTime >= 1 then local chargeSoundClone = chargeSound:Clone() chargeSoundClone.Parent = ToolHandle chargeSoundClone:Play() lastPlayTime = time() table.insert(SoundTable, chargeSoundClone) end wait(1/30) until not Holding
-- Play fire sound local fireSound = ToolHandle:FindFirstChild('Fire') if fireSound then fireSound:Play() end
-- Stop all charge sounds for _, sound in pairs(SoundTable) do sound:Stop() sound:Destroy() end SoundTable = {} end
local function OnButton1Down() local myModel = MyPlayer.Character if Tool.Enabled and myModel and myModel:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and myModel.Humanoid.Health > 0 then ClickTime = time() Holding = true
Tool.MouseButton1Down:FireServer(Mouse.Hit.p) StartInfiniteChargeSound() end end
local function OnButton1Up() Tool.MouseButton1Up:FireServer(Mouse.Hit)
Holding = false end
local function OnEquipped(mouse) Mouse = mouse if Tool.Enabled then Mouse.Icon = MOUSE_ICON else Mouse.Icon = RELOADING_ICON end Mouse.Button1Down:connect(OnButton1Down) Mouse.Button1Up:connect(OnButton1Up) end
-------------------- --| Script Logic |-- --------------------
Tool.Equipped:connect(OnEquipped)
Tool.Changed:connect(function(prop) if prop == 'Enabled' then if Mouse then Mouse.Icon = Tool.Enabled and MOUSE_ICON or RELOADING_ICON end end end)
